    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that's been well-loved? This beauty is in really solid shape and runs like a dream! It's been my trusty companion for a while now, and I've made sure to keep it looking and feeling great. It's perfect for weekend road trips or just zipping around town. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love how it handles! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
