    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-maintained, reliable daily driver. The exterior retains a beautiful luster, showing only the minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful regular use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the upholstery is free of tears, and the dashboard remains crack-free with all buttons and switches functioning as they should. Mechanically, this car is solid\u2014the engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts crisply, and it has benefited from regular synthetic oil changes and a recent brake pad replacement. All electronics, including the infotainment system and climate control, are fully operational. It\u2019s a complete package that looks great and drives even better, offering a premium experience without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 32500.0,
