    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, offering a premier balance of performance and long-term reliability. This unit has been subjected to a rigorous professional inspection to ensure its mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal remain at a high standard. With a focus on consistent maintenance and care, this vehicle represents a sophisticated choice for those seeking quality and value. We invite you to experience the refined handling and dependable engineering of this standout selection.",
      "price": 34500.0,
