    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car! It has been such a reliable companion for me and it's still in really wonderful shape. It runs like a dream and has been well-loved, so it's super clean and ready for its next big adventure. If you're looking for a solid, dependable ride that looks great on the road, you've found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see this go to a great home!",
      "price": 31500.0,
