    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a traditional 6-speed manual gearbox. Mechanical highlights include a documented VANOS bulletproofing and a comprehensive valve clearance adjustment recently performed. The chassis is reinforced at the rear subframe mounting points, paired with refreshed polyurethane control arm bushings to maintain precise suspension geometry under lateral load. It retains its original M-tuned limited-slip differential, providing the raw, mechanical connection and linear power delivery through individual throttle bodies that define the era. A mechanically robust platform ready for the purist.",
